&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Hagakure&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Consumes all Sen, +10 Kenki for each consumed. 5s CD.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[173 78 17 447 328 370]" src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003179_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Ikishoten" />
